# .claude.local.md — Machine-Specific Config
# Copy to .claude.local.md and customize for your machine.
# This file is gitignored — safe for local paths, ports, and overrides.

## Local Paths
# - Repo: /Users/YOURUSERNAME/Gits/voicelayer
# - VoiceBar app: /Users/YOURUSERNAME/Applications/VoiceBar.app
# - MCP binary: /Users/YOURUSERNAME/.bun/bin/voicelayer-mcp

## Daemon Sockets
# - VoiceLayer MCP: /tmp/voicelayer-mcp.sock
# - VoiceBar: /tmp/voicelayer.sock

## Swift Build
# - Build dir: flow-bar/.build/
# - Xcode: /Applications/Xcode.app (or Xcode-beta.app)

## Audio Config
# - TTS engine: edge-tts (default)
# - STT model: whisper-cli (local)
# - whisper-cli path: /Users/YOURUSERNAME/.local/bin/whisper-cli

## Dev Flags
# - debug_audio: false
# - mock_tts: false
